Name: NONOGRAM - KAWAII CUTIES
About the game: This game, called 'NONOGRAM', is a logic puzzle that correctly fills the squares from the given hints. Features Solve the puzzles and complete the 'cute' picture! 6 'cute' pictures and 60 puzzles in total Easy to hard puzzles, from 5x5 to 25x25 Mouse and game controllers are supported.
